item.description: Let's take a walk around the JC Phillips Preserve. I will be bringing my dog and your dog is welcome to join us! The paths may be icy in spots so bring your trakkers if you have some. Park in the lot on the side of the road (RT 97 in Beverly on the Wenham line). JC Phillips is an interesting walk overlooking Wenham Lake. It's an easy walk and pet friendly so we are likely to meet other people walking dogs off leash.
